===== Discovery rule =====

This class is designed to work with network discovery rules. 

<note tip>This API is meant to work with network discovery rules. For the low-level discovery rules see the [[discoveryrule|LLD rule API]].</note>

Object references: \\
  * [[manual:api:reference:drule:object#discovery_rule|Discovery rule]]

Available methods: \\

  * ''[[manual:api:reference:drule:create|drule.create]]'' - create new discovery rules
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:drule:delete|drule.delete]]'' - delete discovery rules
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:drule:get|drule.get]]'' - retrieve discovery rules
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:drule:update|drule.update]]'' - update discovery rules